 rвҶҗTest_InstallAndLoad_096(stopFlag batchFlag);вҺ•TRAP;targetDir;res;zipFilename;rc;msg;targetDir2
вҚқ Install and load a package from a ZIP file first as usual and then in MyApp._tatin
 вҺ•TRAPвҶҗ(999 'C' '. вҚқ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 rвҶҗT._Failed

 #.вҺ•EX TC.GetTatinRootSpace'#'
 #.вҺ•SHADOW'TEMP' вӢ„ 'TEMP'#.вҺ•NS'' вҚқ Used to load stuff into
 targetDirвҶҗвҲҶGetTempDir''
 zipFilenameвҶҗвҲҶTEMP_TEST_DATA,'/ZipWithDeps/aplteam-MyApp1-1.0.0.zip'

 resвҶҗTC.InstallPackages zipFilename targetDir
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'aplteam-MyApp1-1.0.0'вүўвҲҠres
 resвҶҗTC.LoadDependencies targetDir #.TEMP
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'#._tatin.aplteam_MyApp1_1_0_0'вүў' '~вҚЁвҚ•res
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'Universe'вүў#.TEMP.MyApp1.Zoo.Hello3
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 2вү вүў#._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16

 #.вҺ•SHADOW'MyApp' вӢ„ 'MyApp'#.вҺ•NS''
 zipFilenameвҶҗвҲҶTEMP_TEST_DATA,'/CaseTest/example-goo-2.1.0.zip'
 targetDir2вҶҗвҲҶGetTempDir''
 resвҶҗTC.InstallPackages zipFilename targetDir2
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'example-goo-2.1.0'вүўвҲҠres
 resвҶҗTC.LoadDependencies targetDir2 #.MyApp'#.MyApp'
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 0=#.MyApp.вҺ•NC'_tatin'
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 0=#.MyApp._tatin.вҺ•NC'example_goo_2_1_0'
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'Universe'вүў#.MyApp._tatin.example_goo_2_1_0.goo.Hello2
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 1вү вүў#.MyApp._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 2вү вүў#._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16

 rвҶҗT._OK

вҲҶTidyUp:
 (rc msg)вҶҗF.RmDirByForce targetDir
 msg Assert rc=0
 (rc msg)вҶҗF.RmDirByForce targetDir2
 msg Assert rc=0
 #.вҺ•EX TC.GetTatinRootSpace'#'
вҚқDone
